## Server Actions: app/actions

### Dashboard Domain

- `app/actions/dashboard/getBacklog.ts`: Fetches overdue incomplete tasks. Used by dashboard backlog section. Needed to surface pending debt.
- `app/actions/dashboard/getMonthTaskCounts.ts`: Aggregates per-day month counts/completion. Used by calendar month visuals. Needed for efficient calendar stats.
- `app/actions/dashboard/getMonthTasks.ts`: Gets month task rows for day/week rendering. Used by calendar route. Needed for task calendar data.
- `app/actions/dashboard/getStreak.ts`: Computes streak metrics. Used by dashboard stats. Needed for motivation signal.
- `app/actions/dashboard/getSubjectProgress.ts`: Calculates per-subject progress/health/deadline status. Used by dashboard subject cards. Needed for strategic tracking.
- `app/actions/dashboard/getUpcomingDeadlines.ts`: Returns near-term deadline items. Used by dashboard alert list. Needed for urgency awareness.
- `app/actions/dashboard/getWeeklySnapshot.ts`: Fetches current week task snapshot. Used by dashboard weekly section. Needed for weekly overview.
- `app/actions/dashboard/updateProfile.ts`: Updates profile preferences and revalidates relevant routes. Used by settings form. Needed for user configuration persistence.

### Off-Day Domain

- `app/actions/offdays/addOffDay.ts`: Inserts off-day record. Used by onboarding/settings off-day manager. Needed to enforce non-study constraints.
- `app/actions/offdays/deleteOffDay.ts`: Removes off-day record. Used by off-day manager. Needed for correction/editing.
- `app/actions/offdays/getOffDays.ts`: Reads all off-day records. Used by settings/planner setup flows. Needed for constraints display and planning.

### Ops Domain

- `app/actions/ops/getOpsOverview.ts`: Reads telemetry events and aggregates health metrics. Used by operations page. Needed for observability.

### Plan Task Domain

- `app/actions/plan/completeTask.ts`: Marks task complete and updates counters/streak context. Used by dashboard/calendar/timetable task interactions. Needed to record execution.
- `app/actions/plan/createTask.ts`: Creates ad-hoc task with validation. Used by quick-add/calendar forms. Needed for manual planning flexibility.
- `app/actions/plan/rescheduleTask.ts`: Moves task to a new date. Used in drag/drop and reschedule flows. Needed for plan adaptability.
- `app/actions/plan/uncompleteTask.ts`: Reverts completion state. Used where completion toggles exist. Needed for correction workflow.

### Planner Domain

- `app/actions/planner/plan.ts`: Main planning orchestration (analyze/generate/commit/history/reschedule-missed functions). Used by planner wizard and dashboard recovery button. Needed as server-side planning core.
- `app/actions/planner/setup.ts`: Reads/saves planner config, structure, and topic parameters. Used by planner wizard. Needed to persist planner inputs.

### Schedule Domain

- `app/actions/schedule/deleteScheduleTask.ts`: Deletes manual schedule item. Used by schedule page. Needed for cleanup.
- `app/actions/schedule/getWeekSchedule.ts`: Retrieves weekly schedule rows. Used by schedule page. Needed for weekly board data.
- `app/actions/schedule/importPlannerSchedule.ts`: Imports planner-generated tasks into manual schedule context. Used by schedule page action. Needed to bridge planner and execution board.
- `app/actions/schedule/upsertScheduleTask.ts`: Inserts/updates manual schedule tasks. Used by schedule editor flows. Needed for editable schedule persistence.

### Subjects Domain

- `app/actions/subjects/addSubject.ts`: Creates subject. Used by onboarding/subjects/planner editors. Needed as top hierarchy root.
- `app/actions/subjects/chapters.ts`: Chapter/topic-level CRUD/archive helpers. Used by subjects data table. Needed for hierarchy middle layer.
- `app/actions/subjects/deleteSubject.ts`: Deletes subject tree (with relational cascade behavior in DB). Used by subject management UI. Needed for lifecycle completion.
- `app/actions/subjects/getSubjectById.ts`: Fetches single subject details for editing. Used by subject drawers. Needed for edit initialization.
- `app/actions/subjects/reorderChapters.ts`: Persists chapter order changes. Used by drag-drop table. Needed for deterministic display/order.
- `app/actions/subjects/reorderSubjects.ts`: Persists subject order changes. Used by drag-drop table. Needed for custom user prioritization.
- `app/actions/subjects/subtopics.ts`: Subtopic-level CRUD/reorder helpers. Used by hierarchy table. Needed for deeper content breakdown.
- `app/actions/subjects/tasks.ts`: Task-level CRUD/reorder within subject tree. Used by hierarchy table. Needed for actionable leaf nodes.
- `app/actions/subjects/toggleArchiveSubject.ts`: Toggles archive flag on subject. Used by subjects list filters/actions. Needed to hide inactive subjects without deleting.
- `app/actions/subjects/updateSubject.ts`: Updates subject metadata. Used by drawers/planner edits. Needed for maintenance.

