## Architecture Snapshot

This codebase is a Next.js 16 App Router planning platform with Supabase auth/data, server-action-driven domain logic, and a deterministic planner engine. The UI is split into onboarding, management (subjects/settings), planning (wizard), and execution (dashboard/calendar/schedule), with tests focused on action correctness and planning algorithm reliability.
